To comply with enterprise policy, all aged records stored on Network File Share and SharePoint sites must be removed and migrated to Documentum as soon as possible. Non-records should be deleted.

Report Retrieval & Processing
	•	Reports must be pulled by someone with the Network File Share site mapped.
	•	Follow the attached guide to identify aged documents.
	•	Once the report finishes running, open the Excel file received.
	•	Go to the Pivot tab and paste the data into the provided framework.
	•	Filter for all previous years and the upcoming quarter.
	•	Reach out to the respective folder owners (owner details are included in the report).